    {
      "chinese": "[---]\r\n依居住地區劃分為五個亞群：（一）南勢阿美：花蓮市、新城鄉、吉安鄉、壽豐鄉。（二）秀姑巒阿美：鳳林鎮、光復鄉、瑞穗鄉、玉里鎮、富里鄉。（三）海岸阿美：豐濱、長濱鄉、成功鎮以北。（四）馬蘭阿美：成功鎮以南、東河鄉、馬蘭平原一帶等。（五）恆春阿美：鹿野鄉、關山鎮、池上鄉、屏東縣滿州鄉一部份。",
      "ab": "Ano pakainien i aro’ a mipalalikel han i, limaay ko kilac. Sakacecay, o i ’amisay a ’Amis, Nafakoan, Hopo, Yosino, Rinahem. Sakatosa, o i Siwkolanay a ’Amis, Cingalo’an, Fata’an, Kohkoh, Poseko, Kongpo. Sakatolo, o i Sawaliay a ’Amis, Fakong, Kakacawan, i sa’amisan no Madawdaw. Sakasepat, o i Farangaway a ’Amis, Mahawop ko i satimolay no Madawdaw, Fafokod, i masadafdafay no Farangaw maemin. Sakalima, o i Palidaway a ’Amis, Sikano, Cidangcidang, Fanaw, o Palidaw no Pingtong.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2025/04/08/b741b022a164c0e2269b62c0218a709d.mp3",
